title: A Boosted Christmas 2024
author: VD
content_html: Booster Patrol has eight new Christmas carols for your holiday festivities. Here is a link to the YouTube playlist. If you’d like to hear them complete with commentary on UATV, we also played them all on last night’s Darkstream.
